Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:25.84,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\an7\fsp2\fnHYXuanSong 65S\fs45\bord3\blur4\c&H000000&\3c&HFDFDFD&\pos(141.364,425.362)}人類\N{\fs50}哨之盛男
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:55.93,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLanTingHei-DB-GBK\fs39\c&H060E1B&\3c&H40B7CE&\bord2\pos(272,496)}新大{\c&H546227&}陸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:55.93,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fnFZLanTingHei-DB-GBK\fs21\c&H060E1B&\3c&H34AEC5&\bord2\pos(45,615)}那是這片大陸{\c&H546227&}上{\c&H060E1B&}無人知曉的、位於大{\c&H546227&}海{\c&H060E1B&}彼端的新天地。\N被認為建立了與人族比肩的小鬼{\c&H546227&}文{\c&H060E1B&}明。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:14:00.44,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\fnHYXuanSong 65S\fs60\pos(640,576)\bord3\blur4}在破城的基魯聶斯戰敗的——
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:06.98,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\fnHYXuanSong 65S\fs60\pos(640,576)\bord3\blur4}伊瑪古北部平原
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:24.13,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an7\fsp2\fnHYXuanSong 65S\fs45\bord3\blur4\c&H000000&\3c&HF9F9FA&\pos(76.394,429.726)}人類\N{\fs50}黃都第二十四將：荒野之轍丹特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:23.77,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\an7\fsp2\fnHYXuanSong 65S\fs45\bord3\blur4\c&H000000&\3c&HF9F9FA&\pos(443.364,416.029)}人類\N{\fs50}摘果的卡尼亞
